headline: CME Group Inc. Announces Second-Quarter 2025 Earnings Release, Conference Call
summary: CME Group Inc. will announce earnings for the second quarter of 2025 before the markets open on Wednesday, July 23, 2025. Written highlights for the quarter will be posted on the company's website at 6:00 a.m. Central Time, the same time it provides its earnings press release. The company will also hold an investor conference call that day at 7:30 a.m. Central Time, at which time company executives will take analysts' questions.

headline: CME Group to Launch Futures on Mexico's IPC Index
summary: CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today announced it will launch E-Mini S&P BMV IPC Index futures, pending regulatory review.
